## Sign-In and Download

Once you have the Unreal Engine Launcher running, you must sign in and download the current version of the engine.

1. Sign in with your account credentials.

	[REGION:fullwidth]
	![](ue4_installer_login.png)
	[/REGION]

1. The current version of Unreal Engine 4 will begin downloading:

	![](ue4_installer_download.png)

1. Once the download is completed, you can launch Unreal Engine using the **Launch** button:

	![](launch.png)
